<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Windows on Notes</title><link>https://abskmj.github.io/notes/tags/windows/</link><description>Recent content in Windows on Notes</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><copyright>&amp;copy; 2017 abskmj</copyright><lastBuildDate>Wed, 19 May 2021 21:30:00 +0530</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://abskmj.github.io/notes/tags/windows/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Upgrade to WSL2</title><link>https://abskmj.github.io/notes/posts/wsl/upgrade-wsl2/</link><pubDate>Wed, 19 May 2021 21:30:00 +0530</pubDate><guid>https://abskmj.github.io/notes/posts/wsl/upgrade-wsl2/</guid><description>Upgrade an existing version 1 WSL distro to version 2.</description><content>&lt;p>Upgrade an existing version 1 WSL distro to version 2.&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="steps">Steps&lt;/h1>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Open a power shell or cmd terminal&lt;/li>
&lt;li>List distros&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">wsl --list --verbose
&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># output&lt;/span>
NAME STATE VERSION
* Ubuntu Running &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">1&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Upgrade to version 2&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Upgrade can take up to 15 minutes&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">wsl --set-version &amp;lt;distro-name&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">2&lt;/span>
&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># example&lt;/span>
wsl --set-version Ubuntu &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">2&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Check if the upgrade was successful&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">wsl --list --verbose
&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># output&lt;/span>
NAME STATE VERSION
* Ubuntu Running &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">2&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></content></item></channel></rss>